@node Introduction "Introduction to MSys"

  @{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}

      AmigaDOS commands haven't been updated for almost 2 years. They have
  bugs and sometimes could be improved. This package is an attempt to change
  this state of things. All of the supplied commands are 100% compatible
  with AmigaDOS, but also add some new features. In some cases they are
  slightly bigger than their AmigaDOS counterparts, but take no more disk
  space.
      Included in this release are:
  @{"     Avail   " link Doc/avail.doc/main} - Avail command that knows about virtual memory.
  @{"    LoadWB   " link Doc/loadwb.doc/main} - smaller LoadWB command, that can also hide those unwanted
                  'NDOS:???' icons;
  @{"   MakeLink  " link Doc/makelink.doc/main} - creates hard or soft links, capable of detecting circular
                  dependencies;
  @{"    Reboot   " link Doc/reboot.doc/main} - Reboot command with an option to remove resident programs.
  @{"RequestChoice" link Doc/requestchoice.doc/main} - RequestChoice with timeout option.
@endnode

@node Requirements "Requirements for MSys"

  @{b}@{u}Requirements@{uu}@{ub}

      @{"    LoadWB   " link Doc/loadwb.doc/main} requires AmigaDOS 3.0 or higher (@{i}workbench.library @{ui}V39+).
      @{"     Avail   " link Doc/avail.doc/main}, @{"   MakeLink  " link Doc/makelink.doc/main}, @{"    Reboot   " link Doc/reboot.doc/main} and @{"RequestChoice" link Doc/requestchoice.doc/main}
  require AmigaDOS 2.04 or higher (@{i}dos.library @{ui}V37+).
@endnode

@node Installation "Installation of MSys"

  @{b}@{u}Installation@{uu}@{ub}

      Use supplied @{i}Installer @{ui}script to copy necessary files or copy them
  manually to your @{i}C: @{ui} logical device. It is not necessary to make a backup
  copy of commands being replaced. If you want to utilize new @{"  LoadWB  " link Doc/loadwb.doc/main}
  features, you will need to make changes to your @{i}Startup-Sequence@{ui}.
@endnode

@node History "MSys History"

  @{b}@{u}History@{uu}@{ub}

      @{b}Version 1.0 (10.2.96)@{ub} - initial release.

      @{b}Version 1.1 (4.7.96)@{ub}

    Improvements:

    · @{"RequestChoice" link Doc/requestchoice.doc/main} command added.

      @{b}Version 1.2 (9.2.97)@{ub}

    Improvements:

    · @{b}RAMICON@{ub} option added to @{"    LoadWB   " link Doc/requestchoice.doc/main}.
@endnode

